bles en versin trilobular y carcaza especial para reduccin de niveles de ruido.\r\n\r\nLa lnea <strong>CP</strong>, incorpora varias ventajas sobre los modelos equivalentes de la competencia, tales como: Engranes helicoidales, rodamientos de doble hilera de bolas en el lado de engranes, rotores con flechas integrales fabricados en una sola pieza, etc.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/2"][ultimate_heading main_heading="Modelos disponibles con lubricacin aceite-grasa o aceite-aceite"][/ultimate_heading][vc_column_text]\r\n<table class="table">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width="25%"><strong>Modelo</strong></td>\r\n<td width="25%"><strong>CFM </strong></td>\r\n<td width="25%"><strong>BHP </strong></td>\r\n<td width="25%"><strong>Lubricacin aceite-aceite *</strong></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width="25%">2002</td>\r\n<td width="25%">8 - 64</td>\r\n<td width="25%">1.0  5.0</td>\r\n<td width="25%"></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width="25%">2004</td>\r\n<td width="25%">24 - 137</td>\r\n<td width="25%"> 1.0  6.0</td>\r\n<td width="25%"></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width="25%">3002</td>\r\n<td width="25%">22 - 136</td>\r\n<td width="25%">4.0  12.0</td>\r\n<td width="25%">*</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width="25%">3003</td>\r\n<td width="25%">30 - 181</td>\r\n<td width="25%">2.0  15.0</td>\r\n<td width="25%">*</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width="25%">3006</td>\r\n<td width="25%">60 - 310</td>\r\n<td width="25%">5.0  30.0</td>\r\n<td width="25%">*</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width="25%">4002</td>\r\n<td width="25%">18 - 184</td>\r\n<td width="25%">2.0  15.0</td>\r\n<td width="25%">*</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width="25%">4005</td>\r\n<td width="25%">40 - 373</td>\r\n<td width="25%">3.0  32.0</td>\r\n<td width="25%">*</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width="25%">4007</td>\r\n<td width="25%">54 - 492</td>\r\n<td width="25%">4.0  43.0</td>\r\n<td width="25%">*</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width="25%">5003</td>\r\n<td width="25%">41 - 324</td>\r\n<td width