(227, 1, '2017-04-10 12:15:09', '2017-04-10 18:15:09', '[vc_row][vc_column][vc_tta_tour style="flat" shape="square" spacing="" active_section="1" no_fill_content_area="true"][vc_tta_section title="Accesorios" tab_id="accesorios"][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width="2/3"][vc_column_text]\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Filtros y filtros-silenciadores para sopladores, marca <strong>Solberg</strong>, con elementos filtrantes en: celulosa de papel, polister o malla de acero inoxidable.</li>\r\n 	<li>Vlvulas de seguridad marca <strong>Kunkle</strong>.</li>\r\n 	<li>Vlvulas de retencin (check).</li>\r\n 	<li>Motores elctricos <strong>Siemens</strong>.</li>\r\n 	<li>Arrancadores <strong>Siemens</strong>.</li>\r\n 	<li>Variadores de frecuencia <strong>Siemens</strong>.</li>\r\n 	<li>Tableros de control <strong>Siemens</strong>.</li>\r\n 	<li>Interruptores de temperatura y presin.</li>\r\n 	<li>Manmetros y vacumetros.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/3"][porto_carousel stage_padding="0" margin="0" autoplay="yes" autoplay_timeout="5000" items="1" items_lg="1" items_md="1" items_sm="1" items_xs="1" show_dots="yes" dots_pos="nav-inside" dots_align="nav-inside-center"][vc_single_image image="229" img_size="full" alignment="center" onclick="link_image"][vc_single_image image="230" img_size="full" alignment="center" onclick="link_image"][vc_single_image image="240" img_size="full" alignment="center" onclick="link_image"][/porto_carousel][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width="2/3"][ultimate_heading main_heading="Soportes" alignment="left"][/ultimate_heading][vc_column_text]Soportes de tubera tipo omega, fabricados totalmente en acero inoxidable, con barras roscadas que se anclan al piso de concreto y permiten ajustar la altura de la tubera.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/3"][vc_single_image image="231" img_size="full" alignment="center" onclick="link_image"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width="2/3"][ultimate_heading main_heading="Grommets" alignment="left"][/ultimate_heading][vc_column_text]Fabricados en PVC con entrada roscada tipo hembra de  NPT, para tubera de PVC ced. 40, se instalan sobre un barreno de 1  de dimetro.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/3"][vc_single_image image="232" img_size="full" alignment="center" onclick="link_image"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width="2/3"][ultimate_heading main_heading="Silletas de Coneccin Rpida" alignment="left"][/ultimate_heading][vc_column_text]<strong><em>Quick Connect</em></strong>\r\n\r\nPara tuberas de 3  4 de dimetro, fabricadas en polipropileno, permiten una instalacin rpida y fcil de difusores SSI de 9  12 de dimetro, se instalan sobre un barreno de 1  de dimetro.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/3"][vc_single_image image="233" img_size="full" alignment="center" onclick="link_image"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width="2/3"][ultimate_heading main_heading="Juntas de Expansin" alignment="left"][/ultimate_heading][vc_column_text]Para controlar la contraccin y dilatacin trmica de la tuberas fabricadas en pvc con camisa exterior en acero inoxidable.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/3"][porto_carousel stage_padding="0" margin="0" autoplay="yes" autoplay_timeout="5000" items="1" items_lg="1" items_md="1" items_sm="1" items_xs="1" show_dots="yes" dots_pos="nav-inside" dots_align="nav-inside-center"][vc_single_image image="234" img_size="full" alignment="center" onclick="link_image"][vc_single_image image="235" img_size="full" alignment="center" onclick="link_image"][vc_single_image image="236" img_size="full" alignment="center" onclick="link_image"][/porto_carousel][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width="2/3"][ultimate_heading main_heading="Cabina Acstica Marca GIISA" alignment="left"][/ultimate_