atura con termopares en cada cavidad del molde, y as proporcionar un 100% de control de calidad</li>\r\n 	<li>Bajo en contenido de aditivos plastificantes para reducir la contraccin en tamao y su endurecimiento, pero lo suficiente como para evitar su resquebrajamiento</li>\r\n 	<li>Cuerpo en ABS que tolera altas temperaturas, amigable con el medio ambiente, y membrana que resiste temperaturas de hasta 212F (100C)</li>\r\n 	<li>Precios asequibles ya sea como equipo nuevo o para modernizacin de una planta existente.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text]\r\n<table class="table table-striped">\r\n<thead>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th></th>\r\n<th>62x610</th>\r\n<th>62x650</th>\r\n<th>62x762</th>\r\n<th>62x1003</th>\r\n<th>94x502</th>\r\n<th>94x762</th>\r\n<th>94x1003</th>\r\n</tr>\r\n</thead>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Dimetro mm</strong></td>\r\n<td>62 (2.6)</td>\r\n<td>62 (2.6)</td>\r\n<td>62 (2.6)</td>\r\n<td>62 (2.6)</td>\r\n<td>94 (3.7)</td>\r\n<td>94 (3.7)</td>\r\n<td>94 (3.7)</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Largo mm</strong></td>\r\n<td>610 (24)</td>\r\n<td>650 (26)</td>\r\n<td>762 (30)</td>\r\n<td>1003 (39)</td>\r\n<td>502 (20)</td>\r\n<td>762 (30)</td>\r\n<td>1003 (39)</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Flujo de diseo</strong></td>\r\n<td>4.0</td>\r\n<td>4.5</td>\r\n<td>5.0</td>\r\n<td>6.5</td>\r\n<td>4.7</td>\r\n<td>7.5</td>\r\n<td>9.0</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Rango de flujo</strong></td>\r\n<td>2 - 8</td>\r\n<td>2 - 9</td>\r\n<td>3 - 10</td>\r\n<td>3 - 14</td>\r\n<td>4 - 13</td>\r\n<td>7 - 20</td>\r\n<td>9  27</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>No. de perforaciones aprox.</strong></td>\r\n<td>8,050</td>\r\n<td>8,650</td>\r\n<td>10,200</td>\r\n<td>13,770</td>\r\n<td>9,620</td>\r\n<td>15,175</td>\r\n<td>20,400</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>rea de Membrana Activa ft2</strong></td>\r\n<td>1.02</td>\r\n<td>1.07</td>\r\n<td>1.28</td>\r\n<td>1.71</td>\r\n<td>1.25</td>\r\n<td>1.97</td>\r\n<td>2.64</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>